Chavez Says He Called Iran’s Ahmadinejad About U.S. Hostages

-- B y   C h a r l i e   D e v e r e u x
-- 
2011-09-29T18:25:04Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-29/chavez-says-he-called-iran-s-ahmadinejad-about-u-s-hostages.html
Venezuela ’s President  Hugo Chavez 
said he called  Iran ’s President Mahmoud Ahmdinejad about freeing
the U.S. citizens who were arrested while hiking on the
country’s border.  Chavez, speaking on state television, said he made the call
after speaking to the actor Sean Penn.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
